## Getting Started

### Prerequisites

- Java 17+
- Maven 3.9+
- MCP Mesh SDK

### Running the Agent

```bash
mvn spring-boot:run
```

Or with meshctl:

```bash
meshctl start {{ .Name }}
```

The agent will start on port {{ .Port }} by default.

